OL,5,G0030 Michael Palin's Hemingway
OL,6,G     Adventure
OL,7,     F3/4. Michael Palin visits Key
OL,8,     FWest, the southernmost city in the
OL,9,     FUSA, to celebrate Hemingway's
OL,10,     F100th birthday. He also visits the
